title: Woman rescued from metal crate speaks out about captivity | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad 'He put a chain around my neck': Woman held captive for two months in a metal shipping crate breaks her silence about being raped and tortured by a suspected serial killer Kala Brown was found 'chained up like a dog' in a metal shipping container in the backyard of her captor Todd Kohlhepp She watched him kill her boyfriend Charlie Cover, and was held captive Authorities found her when they were searching Kohlhepp's 95-acre property In her first TV interview since the release, she tells Dr Phil McGraw he did not break her Published: 21:44 GMT, 10 February 2017 | Updated: 02:12 GMT, 11 February 2017 576 shares
